Third-party algorithm attributions

The comparison baselines under `baselines/` are independent reimplementations of
third-party drum-difficulty-reduction algorithms, included for reproducible
comparison only:

- `baselines/hopcat.py` / `_hopcat_algo.py` — reimplementation of the HOPCAT
  (C3 CON Tools) drum-reduction algorithm.
- `baselines/onyx.py` / `_onyx_algo.py` — reimplementation of the Onyx Music
  Game Toolkit drum-reduction algorithm.

These reimplementations are the work of this project's authors; the original
algorithms are the work of their respective authors. They are provided for
measuring closeness to Harmonix's official reductions, not as endorsed or
canonical ports.
